<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>yolk_dots Changelog</title><link>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog</link><description>Changelog information for yolk_dots</description><category domain="https://github.com/elkowar/yolk">yolk_dots Changelog</category><atom:link href="http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog.rss" rel="self"/><item><title>0.0.10 - 2024-12-09</title><link>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.10</link><category domain="https://github.com/elkowar/yolk">yolk_dots Changelog</category><guid>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.10</guid><content:encoded><![CDATA[<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>add yolk edit command</li>
<li>Add to_json and from_json lua functions</li>
<li>ensure template expressions are sandboxed</li>
<li>add contains_key, contains_value, regex_captures functions</li>
</ul>
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>join lines in parser where possible</li>
</ul>
<h3>Other</h3>
<ul>
<li>fix clippy warnings</li>
<li>ensure that yolk_templates can deal with missing files</li>
<li>Document inspect.lua library</li>
<li>Add new utility functions to docs</li>
<li>document yolk safeguard and how to clone</li>
<li>simplify parser slightly</li>
<li>enable tagging in release-plz</li>
<li>Update references to replace function</li>
</ul>
]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>0.0.9 - 2024-12-09</title><link>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.9</link><category domain="https://github.com/elkowar/yolk">yolk_dots Changelog</category><guid>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.9</guid><content:encoded><![CDATA[<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>[<strong>breaking</strong>] rename replace to replace_re (r -&gt; rr)</li>
<li>add replace_quoted, replace_value functions</li>
<li>add replace_number tag function</li>
</ul>
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>rename mktmpl to make-template</li>
<li>show proper errors for yolk eval</li>
<li>show source in errors in yolk.lua</li>
<li>parser not preserving newline after conditional end tag</li>
</ul>
<h3>Other</h3>
<ul>
<li>add more tests to lua functions</li>
<li>disable dependency updates in release-plz config</li>
</ul>
]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>v0.0.8</title><link>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.8</link><category domain="https://github.com/elkowar/yolk">yolk_dots Changelog</category><guid>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.8</guid><content:encoded><![CDATA[]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>v0.0.7</title><link>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.7</link><category domain="https://github.com/elkowar/yolk">yolk_dots Changelog</category><guid>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.7</guid><content:encoded><![CDATA[]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>v0.0.5</title><link>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.5</link><category domain="https://github.com/elkowar/yolk">yolk_dots Changelog</category><guid>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.5</guid><content:encoded><![CDATA[]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>v0.0.3</title><link>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.3</link><category domain="https://github.com/elkowar/yolk">yolk_dots Changelog</category><guid>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.3</guid><content:encoded><![CDATA[]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>v0.0.2</title><link>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.2</link><category domain="https://github.com/elkowar/yolk">yolk_dots Changelog</category><guid>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.2</guid><content:encoded><![CDATA[]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>v0.0.1</title><link>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.1</link><category domain="https://github.com/elkowar/yolk">yolk_dots Changelog</category><guid>http://127.0.0.1:7979/yolk/changelog/v0.0.1</guid><content:encoded><![CDATA[]]></content:encoded></item></channel></rss>